txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Monstrous wings taken from the Enemy's scouts, the crebain, in the areas around Echad Dúnann. Deliver the items to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann.
'These enemies will trouble us no longer. Thank you.'
'Our efforts here are ever watched by the foe that soars in the sky. I speak of the crebain. Collect their wings so that these foes can hamper us no longer.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Monstrous Wings
Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann has requested that a collection of monstrous wings be delivered to her.
Deliver the monstrous wings to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann in Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver monstrous wings from the wicked craban-scouts found near Echad Dúnann to the Elf-maid Tinúriel. Tinúriel can be found in Echad Dúnann.
Wanted: Monstrous wings taken from the Enemy's scouts, the crebain, in the areas around Echad Dúnann.
